long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Sunset New Tab is a minimalistic product, that will relax your eyes, every time you open a new tab. Do you want to drift away to some happy memory on the beach, staring at the sunset with your favorite people, Sunset new tab will help you to endeavour on this journey.

By clicking “Add to Chrome”, I accept and agree to installing the Sunset New Tab Chrome extension and setting your New Tab and Search provider to that provided by the service and the Terms of Use and Privacy Policy. The extension will update your search settings and will change your New Tab search services provided by Bing.

With Sunset new tab you will get:
    1. A relaxing change of scenery - an astonishing background image for your new tab page.

    2. The ability to quickly search the web from the new tab. 

Disclaimer: Sunset new tab replaces your default search engine setting. Our product offers enhanced search experience through our partners.
